name: Familia Bendecida
description:
Family is the most precious jewelry, more than gold or pearls. A father has a role to look after, a mother has a role to care for and children always have a way of cultivating love in them.

Although trials and obstacles always come from within and from outside, a little deafness and positive thinking can always be a solution. Love will make the relationship stronger, making the children grow up to be happy souls and full of blessings
